sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Gateway API Gateway<br/>(Envoy Proxy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant ExtProc as Payload Processing<br/>ExtProc Server<br/>9004/TCP gRPC plaintext
    participant ModelResolver as model-provider-resolver<br/>plugin
    participant APITranslation as api-translation<br/>plugin
    participant APIKeyInjection as apikey-injection<br/>plugin
    participant NemoReq as nemo-request-guard<br/>plugin (optional)
    participant NemoResp as nemo-response-guard<br/>plugin (optional)
    participant NemoSvc as NeMo Guardrails<br/>HTTP plaintext
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Provider as External LLM Provider<br/>(OpenAI/Anthropic/Azure/<br/>Bedrock/Vertex)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over K8sAPI,ExtProc: Flow 3: Background Reconciliation (continuous)
    K8sAPI->>ModelResolver: Watch ExternalModel CRs<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Bearer token
    ModelResolver->>ModelResolver: Update modelInfoStore<br/>(in-memory, RWMutex)
    K8sAPI->>APIKeyInjection: Watch labeled Secrets<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Bearer token
    APIKeyInjection->>APIKeyInjection: Update secretStore<br/>(in-memory, RWMutex)

    Note over Client,Provider: Flow 1: External Model Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Client token
    Gateway->>ExtProc: gRPC ExtProc request body<br/>9004/TCP plaintext<br/>(via EnvoyFilter)

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over ExtProc,APIKeyInjection: Plugin Pipeline Processing (CycleState)
        ExtProc->>ModelResolver: ProcessRequest()
        ModelResolver->>ModelResolver: Resolve model name →<br/>provider info from modelInfoStore
        ModelResolver->>ModelResolver: Write provider/credentials<br/>to CycleState

        ExtProc->>APITranslation: ProcessRequest()
        APITranslation->>APITranslation: Read provider type from CycleState
        APITranslation->>APITranslation: Translate OpenAI format →<br/>provider-native format<br/>Rewrite :path header

        ExtProc->>APIKeyInjection: ProcessRequest()
        APIKeyInjection->>APIKeyInjection: Read credential ref from CycleState
        APIKeyInjection->>APIKeyInjection: Lookup API key from secretStore
        APIKeyInjection->>APIKeyInjection: Inject auth header<br/>(Authorization/x-api-key/api-key)
    end

    opt NeMo Guardrails Enabled
        Note over ExtProc,NemoSvc: Flow 2: NeMo Input Guard Check
        ExtProc->>NemoReq: ProcessRequest()
        NemoReq->>NemoSvc: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>HTTP plaintext
        NemoSvc-->>NemoReq: Guard result (allow/block)
        alt Request Blocked
            NemoReq-->>ExtProc: ImmediateResponse (403 Forbidden)
            ExtProc-->>Gateway: gRPC response: 403
            Gateway-->>Client: 403 Forbidden
        end
    end

    ExtProc-->>Gateway: gRPC ExtProc response:<br/>mutated headers + body
    Gateway->>Provider: Translated request<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Injected API key
    Provider-->>Gateway: LLM response<br/>Provider-native format

    Gateway->>ExtProc: gRPC ExtProc response body
    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over ExtProc,NemoResp: Response Processing
        ExtProc->>APITranslation: ProcessResponse()
        APITranslation->>APITranslation: Translate provider-native →<br/>OpenAI format<br/>Strip provider-specific fields

        opt NeMo Guardrails Enabled
            ExtProc->>NemoResp: ProcessResponse()
            NemoResp->>NemoSvc: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>HTTP plaintext
            NemoSvc-->>NemoResp: Guard result (allow/block)
            alt Response Blocked
                NemoResp-->>ExtProc: ImmediateResponse (403)
                ExtProc-->>Gateway: gRPC response: 403
                Gateway-->>Client: 403 Forbidden
            end
        end
    end

    ExtProc-->>Gateway: gRPC ExtProc response:<br/>translated response body
    Gateway-->>Client: OpenAI-format response<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
